body:
Hello there :)

I just had a game on my account which is level 17 (I am levelling up an account to have fun on. I want to have a ranked account and a non-ranked). Champion select was normal. Everyone but one guy called who just locked in his choice (lee sin jungle), and the person who called jungle went support Morgana. I was playing Tristana adc. We got into game and I immediately noticed that everyone on the enemy team, other than Miss Fortune, had keystone masteries. Myself and lux were the people on my team without one. The game started off ok but their Zed was definitely much better than our Lux (sorry Lux). He completely destroyed her in lane and had a ton more cs than her. Then he began roaming everywhere, our morgana went afk and we ended up losing. After the game i check zed&#039;s profile and found out that he was SILVER FIVE. Really? A bunch of low level people who just want to play the game and have fun against a SILVER FIVE? i know that it is not a high rank but to be matched up with him when he had full runes and masteries was very unfair. I had just had a game before with a Xin Xhao jungle on the enemy team who was a smurf and flamed us the whole game for being bad/trash/should unistall etc. 

I was wondering if anyone in the community had any similar games. I&#039;m sorry if this is a bit ranty and not appropriate for this board but it is what riot support suggested.{{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}}
